967 Alabama Department of Economic and Community Affairs shall report to the Chairs of
968 the House Ways and Means-General Fund Committee and the Senate Finance and
969 Taxation-General Fund Committee and the Legislative Fiscal Officer all funds and
970 grants expended specifically in areas with high unemployment and low personal income
971 levels. The report shall detail the amount of funds available in each program and
972 the amount of funds expended in these targeted areas. The Director of the Alabama
973 Department of Economic and Community Affairs shall report within thirty days after
974 the end of each quarter all grants made by the Department in the previous quarter to
