979 Community Affairs shall notify all members of the local legislative delegation five
980 days prior to the announcement of any grant made to any entity located in the
981 legislative jurisdiction. The five days prior notice requirement shall be waived in
982 the event of a declared emergency. The Governor shall encourage the Department to
983 disburse the funds provided herein on a nondiscriminatory basis.
